query:
UPDATE draft_sessions
        SET status = $2,
            current_pick_number = $3,
            time_per_pick_seconds = $4,
            auto_pick_enabled = $5,
            chart_type = $6,
            controlled_team_ids = $7,
            updated_at = $8,
            started_at = $9,
            completed_at = $10
        WHERE id = $1
